    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435364>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435366>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435368>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435370> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435364>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–40: Fig. 32, reproduction of the original drawing of Synedra saxonica (from Kützing 1844: pl. 15, fig. XIV); Fig. 33, reproduction of the original description of Synedra saxonica (from Kützing 1844: 68); Fig. 34, text from catalogue indicated sample 166; Fig. 35. packet for ‘Kützing 166’ (“Salzsee”); Figs 36–38, LM for specimens from BM 18344; Figs 39, 40, reproduction of figure for Synedra pulchella var. saxonica (Kütz.) Grunow in Van Heurck 1881: pl. 41, fig. 3, Fig. 40 the original, Fig. 39, from Van Heurck’s annotated archived copy). Scale bars = 10μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10435364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435366>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41–45: SEM micrographs, Ctenophora saxonica, Fig. 41, internal view of whole valve; Fig. 42, detail of buttressed central area; Figs 43, 44, detail of poles, for rimoportula, virgae and vimines; Fig. 45, external detail of pole with narrow sternum, areolae ornamentation, rimoportula (arrow) and ocellulimbus. Scale bars = 2μm (Figs 42, 43, 45), = 1μm (Fig. 44), = 10μm (Fig. 41)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10435366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435368>
    dc:description "FIGURE 46–49: SEM micrographs, Ctenophora saxonica, Fig. 46, internal view of pole, with rimoportula, ocellulimbus, and striae; Fig. 47, detail of central area from valve and girdle view (arrows); Fig. 48, whole valve in girdle view; Fig. 49, details of VC and copula at pole, plain arrows indicating open bands and dashed arrows their ornamentation. Scale bars = 1μm (Fig. 46), = 2μm (Figs 47, 49), = 10μm (Fig. 48)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10435368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10435370>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50–52: Fig. 50, Exilaria fasciculata sensu Kütz. (1834b [1833]: Dec. VIII, no. 74) in BR; Fig. 51, reproduction of description for E. fasciculata sensu Kützing (1833: 561); Fig. 52, reproduction of drawing for E. fasciculata Kütz. (1834a: taf. 15, fig. 40). Scale bar = 10μm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10435370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

